ğŸ“ Description

This dataset was created to support research and development in automatic sign language interpretation. It includes diverse samples of hands, body posture, and facial expressions to help models capture essential components of sign communication.

The dataset aims to enable:

Sign classification

Gesture recognition

Sequence-to-text translation

Accessibility and assistive technologies

Humanâ€“computer interaction research

